# Pre-commit gate.
#
# Runs ESLint (with --fix + --max-warnings=0) on the staged
# files only — fast, scoped, doesn't punish the developer for
# warnings elsewhere in the repo. Configured via the
# `lint-staged` block in the root package.json.
#
# Bypass with `git commit --no-verify` if you genuinely need
# to land WIP. CLAUDE.md asks not to abuse it — investigate
# the underlying issue first.
pnpm lint-staged
